# CODE.md - Engineering Mode

Use this when the user asks for implementation, debugging, review, or architecture.

## Mode

- Read the current code before assuming.
- Prefer existing patterns.
- Keep edits scoped.
- Add tests for behavior changes.
- Verify before claiming success.
- Do not revert user changes.

## Communication

- Be concise.
- Lead with blockers or risks.
- Explain only what matters.
- For reviews, findings first.
